{"surah":{"number":66,"name":"التحريم","englishName":"At-Tahrim","englishTranslation":"The Prohibition","ayahCount":12},"sources":["Quran.com API v4 (word-by-word Uthmani + English glosses + word audio)","AlQuran.cloud / Tanzil quran-uthmani (independent text verification)","AlQuran.cloud / Saheeh International (flowing English translation)","Quranic Arabic Corpus morphology (word roots)"],"generatedAt":"2026-07-03T04:01:27.657Z","ayahs":[{"number":1,"translation":"O Prophet, why do you prohibit [yourself from] what Allah has made lawful for you, seeking the approval of your wives? And Allah is Forgiving and Merciful.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","english":"O","translit":"yāayyuhā","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلنَّبِىُّ","english":"Prophet","translit":"l-nabiyu","root":"نبأ"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لِمَ","english":"Why (do)","translit":"lima","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُحَرِّمُ","english":"you prohibit","translit":"tuḥarrimu","root":"حرم"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مَآ","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"أَحَلَّ","english":"has made lawful","translit":"aḥalla","root":"حلل"},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahu","root":"أله"},{"position":8,"arabic":"لَكَ ۖ","english":"for you","translit":"laka","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"تَبْتَغِى","english":"seeking","translit":"tabtaghī","root":"بغي","audio":"wbw/066_001_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"مَرْضَاتَ","english":"(to) please","translit":"marḍāta","root":"رضو","audio":"wbw/066_001_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"أَزْوَٰجِكَ ۚ","english":"your wives","translit":"azwājika","root":"زوج","audio":"wbw/066_001_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","english":"And Allah","translit":"wal-lahu","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/066_001_014.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"غَفُورٌۭ","english":"(is) Oft-Forgiving","translit":"ghafūrun","root":"غفر","audio":"wbw/066_001_015.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"رَّحِيمٌۭ","english":"Most Merciful","translit":"raḥīmun","root":"رحم","audio":"wbw/066_001_016.mp3"}]},{"number":2,"translation":"Allah has already ordained for you [Muslims] the dissolution of your oaths. And Allah is your protector, and He is the Knowing, the Wise.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"قَدْ","english":"Indeed","translit":"qad","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"فَرَضَ","english":"has ordained","translit":"faraḍa","root":"فرض"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahu","root":"أله"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","english":"for you","translit":"lakum","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"تَحِلَّةَ","english":"(the) dissolution","translit":"taḥillata","root":"حلل"},{"position":6,"arabic":"أَيْمَـٰنِكُمْ ۚ","english":"(of) your oaths","translit":"aymānikum","root":"يمن"},{"position":7,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","english":"And Allah","translit":"wal-lahu","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/066_002_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"مَوْلَىٰكُمْ ۖ","english":"(is) your Protector","translit":"mawlākum","root":"ولي","audio":"wbw/066_002_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"وَهُوَ","english":"and He","translit":"wahuwa","root":"","audio":"wbw/066_002_011.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلْعَلِيمُ","english":"(is) the All-Knower","translit":"l-ʿalīmu","root":"علم","audio":"wbw/066_002_012.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلْحَكِيمُ","english":"the All-Wise","translit":"l-ḥakīmu","root":"حكم","audio":"wbw/066_002_013.mp3"}]},{"number":3,"translation":"And [remember] when the Prophet confided to one of his wives a statement; and when she informed [another] of it and Allah showed it to him, he made known part of it and ignored a part. And when he informed her about it, she said, \"Who told you this?\" He said, \"I was informed by the Knowing, the Acquainted.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذْ","english":"And when","translit":"wa-idh","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَسَرَّ","english":"confided","translit":"asarra","root":"سرر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلنَّبِىُّ","english":"the Prophet","translit":"l-nabiyu","root":"نبأ"},{"position":4,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","english":"to","translit":"ilā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"بَعْضِ","english":"one","translit":"baʿḍi","root":"بعض"},{"position":6,"arabic":"أَزْوَٰجِهِۦ","english":"(of) his wives","translit":"azwājihi","root":"زوج"},{"position":7,"arabic":"حَدِيثًۭا","english":"a statement","translit":"ḥadīthan","root":"حدث"},{"position":8,"arabic":"فَلَمَّا","english":"and when","translit":"falammā","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"نَبَّأَتْ","english":"she informed","translit":"nabba-at","root":"نبأ"},{"position":10,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","english":"about it","translit":"bihi","root":""},{"position":11,"arabic":"وَأَظْهَرَهُ","english":"and made it apparent","translit":"wa-aẓharahu","root":"ظهر"},{"position":12,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahu","root":"أله"},{"position":13,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِ","english":"to him","translit":"ʿalayhi","root":""},{"position":14,"arabic":"عَرَّفَ","english":"he made known","translit":"ʿarrafa","root":"عرف"},{"position":15,"arabic":"بَعْضَهُۥ","english":"a part of it","translit":"baʿḍahu","root":"بعض"},{"position":16,"arabic":"وَأَعْرَضَ","english":"and avoided","translit":"wa-aʿraḍa","root":"عرض"},{"position":17,"arabic":"عَنۢ","english":"[of]","translit":"ʿan","root":""},{"position":18,"arabic":"بَعْضٍۢ ۖ","english":"a part","translit":"baʿḍin","root":"بعض"},{"position":19,"arabic":"فَلَمَّا","english":"Then when","translit":"falammā","root":"","audio":"wbw/066_003_020.mp3"},{"position":20,"arabic":"نَبَّأَهَا","english":"he informed her","translit":"nabba-ahā","root":"نبأ","audio":"wbw/066_003_021.mp3"},{"position":21,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","english":"about it","translit":"bihi","root":"","audio":"wbw/066_003_022.mp3"},{"position":22,"arabic":"قَالَتْ","english":"she said","translit":"qālat","root":"قول","audio":"wbw/066_003_023.mp3"},{"position":23,"arabic":"مَنْ","english":"Who","translit":"man","root":"","audio":"wbw/066_003_024.mp3"},{"position":24,"arabic":"أَنۢبَأَكَ","english":"informed you","translit":"anba-aka","root":"نبأ","audio":"wbw/066_003_025.mp3"},{"position":25,"arabic":"هَـٰذَا ۖ","english":"this","translit":"hādhā","root":"","audio":"wbw/066_003_026.mp3"},{"position":26,"arabic":"قَالَ","english":"He said","translit":"qāla","root":"قول","audio":"wbw/066_003_028.mp3"},{"position":27,"arabic":"نَبَّأَنِىَ","english":"Has informed me","translit":"nabba-aniya","root":"نبأ","audio":"wbw/066_003_029.mp3"},{"position":28,"arabic":"ٱلْعَلِيمُ","english":"the All-Knower","translit":"l-ʿalīmu","root":"علم","audio":"wbw/066_003_030.mp3"},{"position":29,"arabic":"ٱلْخَبِيرُ","english":"the All-Aware","translit":"l-khabīru","root":"خبر","audio":"wbw/066_003_031.mp3"}]},{"number":4,"translation":"If you two [wives] repent to Allah, [it is best], for your hearts have deviated. But if you cooperate against him - then indeed Allah is his protector, and Gabriel and the righteous of the believers and the angels, moreover, are [his] assistants.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِن","english":"If","translit":"in","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"تَتُوبَآ","english":"you both turn","translit":"tatūbā","root":"توب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"إِلَى","english":"to","translit":"ilā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":5,"arabic":"فَقَدْ","english":"so indeed","translit":"faqad","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"صَغَتْ","english":"(are) inclined","translit":"ṣaghat","root":"صغو"},{"position":7,"arabic":"قُلُوبُكُمَا ۖ","english":"your hearts","translit":"qulūbukumā","root":"قلب"},{"position":8,"arabic":"وَإِن","english":"but if","translit":"wa-in","root":"","audio":"wbw/066_004_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"تَظَـٰهَرَا","english":"you backup each other","translit":"taẓāharā","root":"ظهر","audio":"wbw/066_004_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِ","english":"against him","translit":"ʿalayhi","root":"","audio":"wbw/066_004_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"فَإِنَّ","english":"then indeed","translit":"fa-inna","root":"","audio":"wbw/066_004_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-laha","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/066_004_013.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"هُوَ","english":"He","translit":"huwa","root":"","audio":"wbw/066_004_014.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"مَوْلَىٰهُ","english":"(is) his Protector","translit":"mawlāhu","root":"ولي","audio":"wbw/066_004_015.mp3"},{"position":15,"arabic":"وَجِبْرِيلُ","english":"and Jibreel","translit":"wajib'rīlu","root":"","audio":"wbw/066_004_016.mp3"},{"position":16,"arabic":"وَصَـٰلِحُ","english":"and (the) righteous","translit":"waṣāliḥu","root":"صلح","audio":"wbw/066_004_017.mp3"},{"position":17,"arabic":"ٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَ ۖ","english":"believers","translit":"l-mu'minīna","root":"أمن","audio":"wbw/066_004_018.mp3"},{"position":18,"arabic":"وَٱلْمَلَـٰٓئِكَةُ","english":"and the Angels","translit":"wal-malāikatu","root":"ملك","audio":"wbw/066_004_020.mp3"},{"position":19,"arabic":"بَعْدَ","english":"after","translit":"baʿda","root":"بعد","audio":"wbw/066_004_021.mp3"},{"position":20,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","english":"that","translit":"dhālika","root":"","audio":"wbw/066_004_022.mp3"},{"position":21,"arabic":"ظَهِيرٌ","english":"(are his) assistants","translit":"ẓahīrun","root":"ظهر","audio":"wbw/066_004_023.mp3"}]},{"number":5,"translation":"Perhaps his Lord, if he divorced you [all], would substitute for him wives better than you - submitting [to Allah], believing, devoutly obedient, repentant, worshipping, and traveling - [ones] previously married and virgins.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"عَسَىٰ","english":"Perhaps","translit":"ʿasā","root":"عسي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"رَبُّهُۥٓ","english":"his Lord","translit":"rabbuhu","root":"ربب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"إِن","english":"if","translit":"in","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"طَلَّقَكُنَّ","english":"he divorced you","translit":"ṭallaqakunna","root":"طلق"},{"position":5,"arabic":"أَن","english":"[that]","translit":"an","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"يُبْدِلَهُۥٓ","english":"He will substitute for him","translit":"yub'dilahu","root":"بدل"},{"position":7,"arabic":"أَزْوَٰجًا","english":"wives","translit":"azwājan","root":"زوج"},{"position":8,"arabic":"خَيْرًۭا","english":"better","translit":"khayran","root":"خير"},{"position":9,"arabic":"مِّنكُنَّ","english":"than you","translit":"minkunna","root":""},{"position":10,"arabic":"مُسْلِمَـٰتٍۢ","english":"submissive","translit":"mus'limātin","root":"سلم"},{"position":11,"arabic":"مُّؤْمِنَـٰتٍۢ","english":"faithful","translit":"mu'minātin","root":"أمن"},{"position":12,"arabic":"قَـٰنِتَـٰتٍۢ","english":"obedient","translit":"qānitātin","root":"قنت"},{"position":13,"arabic":"تَـٰٓئِبَـٰتٍ","english":"repentant","translit":"tāibātin","root":"توب"},{"position":14,"arabic":"عَـٰبِدَٰتٍۢ","english":"who worship","translit":"ʿābidātin","root":"عبد"},{"position":15,"arabic":"سَـٰٓئِحَـٰتٍۢ","english":"who fast","translit":"sāiḥātin","root":"سيح"},{"position":16,"arabic":"ثَيِّبَـٰتٍۢ","english":"previously married","translit":"thayyibātin","root":"ثيب"},{"position":17,"arabic":"وَأَبْكَارًۭا","english":"and virgins","translit":"wa-abkāran","root":"بكر"}]},{"number":6,"translation":"O you who have believed, protect yourselves and your families from a Fire whose fuel is people and stones, over which are [appointed] angels, harsh and severe; they do not disobey Allah in what He commands them but do what they are commanded.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","english":"O","translit":"yāayyuhā","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","english":"(you) who","translit":"alladhīna","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","english":"believe","translit":"āmanū","root":"أمن"},{"position":4,"arabic":"قُوٓا۟","english":"Protect","translit":"qū","root":"وقي"},{"position":5,"arabic":"أَنفُسَكُمْ","english":"yourselves","translit":"anfusakum","root":"نفس"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَأَهْلِيكُمْ","english":"and your families","translit":"wa-ahlīkum","root":"أهل"},{"position":7,"arabic":"نَارًۭا","english":"(from) a Fire","translit":"nāran","root":"نور"},{"position":8,"arabic":"وَقُودُهَا","english":"whose fuel","translit":"waqūduhā","root":"وقد"},{"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلنَّاسُ","english":"(is) people","translit":"l-nāsu","root":"أنس"},{"position":10,"arabic":"وَٱلْحِجَارَةُ","english":"and stones","translit":"wal-ḥijāratu","root":"حجر"},{"position":11,"arabic":"عَلَيْهَا","english":"over it","translit":"ʿalayhā","root":""},{"position":12,"arabic":"مَلَـٰٓئِكَةٌ","english":"(are) Angels","translit":"malāikatun","root":"ملك"},{"position":13,"arabic":"غِلَاظٌۭ","english":"stern","translit":"ghilāẓun","root":"غلظ"},{"position":14,"arabic":"شِدَادٌۭ","english":"severe","translit":"shidādun","root":"شدد"},{"position":15,"arabic":"لَّا","english":"not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":16,"arabic":"يَعْصُونَ","english":"they disobey","translit":"yaʿṣūna","root":"عصي"},{"position":17,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-laha","root":"أله"},{"position":18,"arabic":"مَآ","english":"(in) what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":19,"arabic":"أَمَرَهُمْ","english":"He Commands them","translit":"amarahum","root":"أمر"},{"position":20,"arabic":"وَيَفْعَلُونَ","english":"but they do","translit":"wayafʿalūna","root":"فعل"},{"position":21,"arabic":"مَا","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":22,"arabic":"يُؤْمَرُونَ","english":"they are commanded","translit":"yu'marūna","root":"أمر"}]},{"number":7,"translation":"O you who have disbelieved, make no excuses that Day. You will only be recompensed for what you used to do.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","english":"O","translit":"yāayyuhā","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","english":"(you) who","translit":"alladhīna","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"كَفَرُوا۟","english":"disbelieve","translit":"kafarū","root":"كفر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لَا","english":"(Do) not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"تَعْتَذِرُوا۟","english":"make excuses","translit":"taʿtadhirū","root":"عذر"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْيَوْمَ ۖ","english":"today","translit":"l-yawma","root":"يوم"},{"position":7,"arabic":"إِنَّمَا","english":"Only","translit":"innamā","root":"","audio":"wbw/066_007_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"تُجْزَوْنَ","english":"you will be recompensed","translit":"tuj'zawna","root":"جزي","audio":"wbw/066_007_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"مَا","english":"(for) what","translit":"mā","root":"","audio":"wbw/066_007_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"كُنتُمْ","english":"you used to","translit":"kuntum","root":"كون","audio":"wbw/066_007_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"تَعْمَلُونَ","english":"do","translit":"taʿmalūna","root":"عمل","audio":"wbw/066_007_012.mp3"}]},{"number":8,"translation":"O you who have believed, repent to Allah with sincere repentance. Perhaps your Lord will remove from you your misdeeds and admit you into gardens beneath which rivers flow [on] the Day when Allah will not disgrace the Prophet and those who believed with him. Their light will proceed before them and on their right; they will say, \"Our Lord, perfect for us our light and forgive us. Indeed, You are over all things competent.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","english":"O","translit":"yāayyuhā","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","english":"(you) who believe","translit":"alladhīna","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","english":"believe","translit":"āmanū","root":"أمن"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُوبُوٓا۟","english":"Turn","translit":"tūbū","root":"توب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"إِلَى","english":"to","translit":"ilā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":7,"arabic":"تَوْبَةًۭ","english":"(in) repentance","translit":"tawbatan","root":"توب"},{"position":8,"arabic":"نَّصُوحًا","english":"sincere","translit":"naṣūḥan","root":"نصح"},{"position":9,"arabic":"عَسَىٰ","english":"Perhaps","translit":"ʿasā","root":"عسي"},{"position":10,"arabic":"رَبُّكُمْ","english":"your Lord","translit":"rabbukum","root":"ربب"},{"position":11,"arabic":"أَن","english":"will","translit":"an","root":""},{"position":12,"arabic":"يُكَفِّرَ","english":"remove","translit":"yukaffira","root":"كفر"},{"position":13,"arabic":"عَنكُمْ","english":"from you","translit":"ʿankum","root":""},{"position":14,"arabic":"سَيِّـَٔاتِكُمْ","english":"your evil deeds","translit":"sayyiātikum","root":"سوأ"},{"position":15,"arabic":"وَيُدْخِلَكُمْ","english":"and admit you","translit":"wayud'khilakum","root":"دخل"},{"position":16,"arabic":"جَنَّـٰتٍۢ","english":"(into) Gardens","translit":"jannātin","root":"جنن"},{"position":17,"arabic":"تَجْرِى","english":"flow","translit":"tajrī","root":"جري"},{"position":18,"arabic":"مِن","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":19,"arabic":"تَحْتِهَا","english":"underneath it","translit":"taḥtihā","root":"تحت"},{"position":20,"arabic":"ٱلْأَنْهَـٰرُ","english":"the rivers","translit":"l-anhāru","root":"نهر"},{"position":21,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","english":"(on the) Day","translit":"yawma","root":"يوم"},{"position":22,"arabic":"لَا","english":"not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":23,"arabic":"يُخْزِى","english":"will be disgraced","translit":"yukh'zī","root":"خزي"},{"position":24,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","english":"(by) Allah","translit":"l-lahu","root":"أله"},{"position":25,"arabic":"ٱلنَّبِىَّ","english":"the Prophet","translit":"l-nabiya","root":"نبأ"},{"position":26,"arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ","english":"and those who","translit":"wa-alladhīna","root":""},{"position":27,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","english":"believed","translit":"āmanū","root":"أمن"},{"position":28,"arabic":"مَعَهُۥ ۖ","english":"with him","translit":"maʿahu","root":""},{"position":29,"arabic":"نُورُهُمْ","english":"Their light","translit":"nūruhum","root":"نور","audio":"wbw/066_008_030.mp3"},{"position":30,"arabic":"يَسْعَىٰ","english":"will run","translit":"yasʿā","root":"سعي","audio":"wbw/066_008_031.mp3"},{"position":31,"arabic":"بَيْنَ","english":"before","translit":"bayna","root":"بين","audio":"wbw/066_008_032.mp3"},{"position":32,"arabic":"أَيْدِيهِمْ","english":"their hands","translit":"aydīhim","root":"يدي","audio":"wbw/066_008_033.mp3"},{"position":33,"arabic":"وَبِأَيْمَـٰنِهِمْ","english":"and on their right","translit":"wabi-aymānihim","root":"يمن","audio":"wbw/066_008_034.mp3"},{"position":34,"arabic":"يَقُولُونَ","english":"they will say","translit":"yaqūlūna","root":"قول","audio":"wbw/066_008_035.mp3"},{"position":35,"arabic":"رَبَّنَآ","english":"Our Lord","translit":"rabbanā","root":"ربب","audio":"wbw/066_008_036.mp3"},{"position":36,"arabic":"أَتْمِمْ","english":"Perfect","translit":"atmim","root":"تمم","audio":"wbw/066_008_037.mp3"},{"position":37,"arabic":"لَنَا","english":"for us","translit":"lanā","root":"","audio":"wbw/066_008_038.mp3"},{"position":38,"arabic":"نُورَنَا","english":"our light","translit":"nūranā","root":"نور","audio":"wbw/066_008_039.mp3"},{"position":39,"arabic":"وَٱغْفِرْ","english":"and grant forgiveness","translit":"wa-igh'fir","root":"غفر","audio":"wbw/066_008_040.mp3"},{"position":40,"arabic":"لَنَآ ۖ","english":"to us","translit":"lanā","root":"","audio":"wbw/066_008_041.mp3"},{"position":41,"arabic":"إِنَّكَ","english":"Indeed, You","translit":"innaka","root":"","audio":"wbw/066_008_043.mp3"},{"position":42,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","english":"(are) over","translit":"ʿalā","root":"","audio":"wbw/066_008_044.mp3"},{"position":43,"arabic":"كُلِّ","english":"every","translit":"kulli","root":"كلل","audio":"wbw/066_008_045.mp3"},{"position":44,"arabic":"شَىْءٍۢ","english":"thing","translit":"shayin","root":"شيأ","audio":"wbw/066_008_046.mp3"},{"position":45,"arabic":"قَدِيرٌۭ","english":"All-Powerful","translit":"qadīrun","root":"قدر","audio":"wbw/066_008_047.mp3"}]},{"number":9,"translation":"O Prophet, strive against the disbelievers and the hypocrites and be harsh upon them. And their refuge is Hell, and wretched is the destination.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","english":"O","translit":"yāayyuhā","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلنَّبِىُّ","english":"Prophet","translit":"l-nabiyu","root":"نبأ"},{"position":3,"arabic":"جَـٰهِدِ","english":"Strive","translit":"jāhidi","root":"جهد"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْكُفَّارَ","english":"(against) the disbelievers","translit":"l-kufāra","root":"كفر"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَٱلْمُنَـٰفِقِينَ","english":"and the hypocrites","translit":"wal-munāfiqīna","root":"نفق"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَٱغْلُظْ","english":"and be stern","translit":"wa-ugh'luẓ","root":"غلظ"},{"position":7,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِمْ ۚ","english":"with them","translit":"ʿalayhim","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"وَمَأْوَىٰهُمْ","english":"And their abode","translit":"wamawāhum","root":"أوي","audio":"wbw/066_009_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"جَهَنَّمُ ۖ","english":"(is) Hell","translit":"jahannamu","root":"","audio":"wbw/066_009_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"وَبِئْسَ","english":"and wretched is","translit":"wabi'sa","root":"بأس","audio":"wbw/066_009_012.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلْمَصِيرُ","english":"the destination","translit":"l-maṣīru","root":"صير","audio":"wbw/066_009_013.mp3"}]},{"number":10,"translation":"Allah presents an example of those who disbelieved: the wife of Noah and the wife of Lot. They were under two of Our righteous servants but betrayed them, so those prophets did not avail them from Allah at all, and it was said, \"Enter the Fire with those who enter.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ضَرَبَ","english":"Presents","translit":"ḍaraba","root":"ضرب"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahu","root":"أله"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَثَلًۭا","english":"an example","translit":"mathalan","root":"مثل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لِّلَّذِينَ","english":"for those who","translit":"lilladhīna","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"كَفَرُوا۟","english":"disbelieved","translit":"kafarū","root":"كفر"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱمْرَأَتَ","english":"(the) wife","translit":"im'ra-ata","root":"مرأ"},{"position":7,"arabic":"نُوحٍۢ","english":"(of) Nuh","translit":"nūḥin","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"وَٱمْرَأَتَ","english":"(and the) wife","translit":"wa-im'ra-ata","root":"مرأ"},{"position":9,"arabic":"لُوطٍۢ ۖ","english":"(of) Lut","translit":"lūṭin","root":""},{"position":10,"arabic":"كَانَتَا","english":"They were","translit":"kānatā","root":"كون","audio":"wbw/066_010_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"تَحْتَ","english":"under","translit":"taḥta","root":"تحت","audio":"wbw/066_010_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"عَبْدَيْنِ","english":"two [slaves]","translit":"ʿabdayni","root":"عبد","audio":"wbw/066_010_013.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"مِنْ","english":"of","translit":"min","root":"","audio":"wbw/066_010_014.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"عِبَادِنَا","english":"Our slaves","translit":"ʿibādinā","root":"عبد","audio":"wbw/066_010_015.mp3"},{"position":15,"arabic":"صَـٰلِحَيْنِ","english":"righteous","translit":"ṣāliḥayni","root":"صلح","audio":"wbw/066_010_016.mp3"},{"position":16,"arabic":"فَخَانَتَاهُمَا","english":"but they both betrayed them","translit":"fakhānatāhumā","root":"خون","audio":"wbw/066_010_017.mp3"},{"position":17,"arabic":"فَلَمْ","english":"so not","translit":"falam","root":"","audio":"wbw/066_010_018.mp3"},{"position":18,"arabic":"يُغْنِيَا","english":"they availed","translit":"yugh'niyā","root":"غني","audio":"wbw/066_010_019.mp3"},{"position":19,"arabic":"عَنْهُمَا","english":"both of them","translit":"ʿanhumā","root":"","audio":"wbw/066_010_020.mp3"},{"position":20,"arabic":"مِنَ","english":"from","translit":"mina","root":"","audio":"wbw/066_010_021.mp3"},{"position":21,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/066_010_022.mp3"},{"position":22,"arabic":"شَيْـًۭٔا","english":"(in) anything","translit":"shayan","root":"شيأ","audio":"wbw/066_010_023.mp3"},{"position":23,"arabic":"وَقِيلَ","english":"and it was said","translit":"waqīla","root":"قول","audio":"wbw/066_010_024.mp3"},{"position":24,"arabic":"ٱدْخُلَا","english":"Enter","translit":"ud'khulā","root":"دخل","audio":"wbw/066_010_025.mp3"},{"position":25,"arabic":"ٱلنَّارَ","english":"the Fire","translit":"l-nāra","root":"نور","audio":"wbw/066_010_026.mp3"},{"position":26,"arabic":"مَعَ","english":"with","translit":"maʿa","root":"","audio":"wbw/066_010_027.mp3"},{"position":27,"arabic":"ٱلدَّٰخِلِينَ","english":"those who enter","translit":"l-dākhilīna","root":"دخل","audio":"wbw/066_010_028.mp3"}]},{"number":11,"translation":"And Allah presents an example of those who believed: the wife of Pharaoh, when she said, \"My Lord, build for me near You a house in Paradise and save me from Pharaoh and his deeds and save me from the wrongdoing people.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَضَرَبَ","english":"And presents","translit":"waḍaraba","root":"ضرب"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahu","root":"أله"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَثَلًۭا","english":"an example","translit":"mathalan","root":"مثل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لِّلَّذِينَ","english":"for those who","translit":"lilladhīna","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","english":"believed","translit":"āmanū","root":"أمن"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱمْرَأَتَ","english":"(the) wife","translit":"im'ra-ata","root":"مرأ"},{"position":7,"arabic":"فِرْعَوْنَ","english":"(of) Firaun","translit":"fir'ʿawna","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"إِذْ","english":"when","translit":"idh","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"قَالَتْ","english":"she said","translit":"qālat","root":"قول"},{"position":10,"arabic":"رَبِّ","english":"My Lord","translit":"rabbi","root":"ربب"},{"position":11,"arabic":"ٱبْنِ","english":"Build","translit":"ib'ni","root":"بني"},{"position":12,"arabic":"لِى","english":"for me","translit":"lī","root":""},{"position":13,"arabic":"عِندَكَ","english":"near You","translit":"ʿindaka","root":"عند"},{"position":14,"arabic":"بَيْتًۭا","english":"a house","translit":"baytan","root":"بيت"},{"position":15,"arabic":"فِى","english":"in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":16,"arabic":"ٱلْجَنَّةِ","english":"Paradise","translit":"l-janati","root":"جنن"},{"position":17,"arabic":"وَنَجِّنِى","english":"and save me","translit":"wanajjinī","root":"نجو"},{"position":18,"arabic":"مِن","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":19,"arabic":"فِرْعَوْنَ","english":"Firaun","translit":"fir'ʿawna","root":""},{"position":20,"arabic":"وَعَمَلِهِۦ","english":"and his deeds","translit":"waʿamalihi","root":"عمل"},{"position":21,"arabic":"وَنَجِّنِى","english":"and save me","translit":"wanajjinī","root":"نجو"},{"position":22,"arabic":"مِنَ","english":"from","translit":"mina","root":""},{"position":23,"arabic":"ٱلْقَوْمِ","english":"the people","translit":"l-qawmi","root":"قوم"},{"position":24,"arabic":"ٱلظَّـٰلِمِينَ","english":"the wrongdoers","translit":"l-ẓālimīna","root":"ظلم"}]},{"number":12,"translation":"And [the example of] Mary, the daughter of 'Imran, who guarded her chastity, so We blew into [her garment] through Our angel, and she believed in the words of her Lord and His scriptures and was of the devoutly obedient.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَرْيَمَ","english":"And Maryam","translit":"wamaryama","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱبْنَتَ","english":"(the) daughter","translit":"ib'nata","root":"بني"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عِمْرَٰنَ","english":"(of) Imran","translit":"ʿim'rāna","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلَّتِىٓ","english":"who","translit":"allatī","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"أَحْصَنَتْ","english":"guarded","translit":"aḥṣanat","root":"حصن"},{"position":6,"arabic":"فَرْجَهَا","english":"her chastity","translit":"farjahā","root":"فرج"},{"position":7,"arabic":"فَنَفَخْنَا","english":"so We breathed","translit":"fanafakhnā","root":"نفخ"},{"position":8,"arabic":"فِيهِ","english":"into it","translit":"fīhi","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"مِن","english":"of","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":10,"arabic":"رُّوحِنَا","english":"Our Spirit","translit":"rūḥinā","root":"روح"},{"position":11,"arabic":"وَصَدَّقَتْ","english":"And she believed","translit":"waṣaddaqat","root":"صدق"},{"position":12,"arabic":"بِكَلِمَـٰتِ","english":"(in the) Words","translit":"bikalimāti","root":"كلم"},{"position":13,"arabic":"رَبِّهَا","english":"(of) her Lord","translit":"rabbihā","root":"ربب"},{"position":14,"arabic":"وَكُتُبِهِۦ","english":"and His Books","translit":"wakutubihi","root":"كتب"},{"position":15,"arabic":"وَكَانَتْ","english":"and she was","translit":"wakānat","root":"كون"},{"position":16,"arabic":"مِنَ","english":"of","translit":"mina","root":""},{"position":17,"arabic":"ٱلْقَـٰنِتِينَ","english":"the devoutly obedient","translit":"l-qānitīna","root":"قنت"}]}]}
